iant of M.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 0aInvariants. 0aThree-manifolds (Topology). 7aMATHEMATICS / Topology.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPrinceton Annals of Mathematics eBook-Package 1940-2020z978311049491408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPrinceton University Press eBook-Package Archive 1927-1999z978311044249640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978140088246540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781400882465423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781400882465.jpg  a978-3-11-044249-6  Princeton University Press eBook-Package Archive 1927-1999c1927d1999  a978-3-11-049491-4  Princeton Annals of Mathematics eBook-Package 1940-2020  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MTPY  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_MTPY  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA18STMEE  aPDA5EBK